re this with the equivalence of deterministic time and reversible time, which is simply shown by storing the whole computational history on a separate write-only tape <ref> [Le63, Be89] </ref>. It is remarkable that this is the very same construction which proves the equivalence of nondeterministic time and symmetric 1 time [LePa82].
